{"tid":1957660,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"【幫推】散仔協會2017年搞3萬人的「撐警大會」，沒有申請不反對通知書，涉嫌違法","createTime":"2020-04-04T05:33:07.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-04T05:41:04.000Z","uid":48040,"like":5,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"76e1805458fd17bfc2b4b9ed8e558131f65e4990","tid":1957660,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:33:07.000Z","msg":"非法集結。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/73732/%E4%B8%83%E8%AD%A6%E6%A1%88-%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6-%E6%9C%83%E5%93%A1%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83-3-3%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD-%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E8%80%85-%E8%A6%81%E7%B7%A0%E9%80%A0%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%25A4%25BE%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2596%25B0%25E8%2581%259E%2F73732%2F%25E4%25B8%2583%25E8%25AD%25A6%25E6%25A1%2588-%25E6%2592%2590%25E8%25AD%25A6-%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%2593%25A1%25E5%25A4%25A7%25E6%259C%2583-3-3%25E8%2590%25AC%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AD-%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%25B8%25AD%25E8%2580%2585-%25E8%25A6%2581%25E7%25B7%25A0%25E9%2580%25A0%25E6%25AD%25B7%25E5%258F%25B2&d=dfx5yx0%2Fy135WOof7TdQysg7Fotki3H%2BSmgHlFrgEoM%3D&h=9db8fa83\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%A4%BE%E6%9C%83%E6%96%B0%E8%81%9E/73732/%E4%B8%83%E8%AD%A6%E6%A1%88-%E6%92%90%E8%AD%A6-%E6%9C%83%E5%93%A1%E5%A4%A7%E6%9C%83-3-3%E8%90%AC%E4%BA%BA%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD-%E5%87%BA%E5%B8%AD%E8%80%85-%E8%A6%81%E7%B7%A0%E9%80%A0%E6%AD%B7%E5%8F%B2</a><br />\n<br />\n就今次並無申請不反對通知書，而有3.3萬人集會，陳祖光在活動結束後強調，今次只是「協會代表大會」，屬內部事務，非隨便人能進入，而所有會員均有權出席，並非《公安條例》所規管的「集會」，又指人數是他始料不及。<br />\n<br />\n民權觀察成員沈偉男質疑，《公安條例》第7條列明，只有500人以下的私人集會才毋須取得不反對通知書，過往亦有遊行示威的組織者因人數遠超預期而被警方警告，故今次會員大會有觸犯條例之嫌。"},{"pid":"d10d8caed3efa3d60cf724fe5e18f19690845332","tid":1957660,"uid":205162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:33:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3de1af2b53572c470995e49da1e0289f748bb2da","tid":1957660,"uid":48040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:35:50.000Z","msg":"葉劉淑儀、梁美芬、何君堯都有出席，均可能涉嫌非法集結。"},{"pid":"ac507df064c51dbb8b8e915edd0a7021d5a2cccc","tid":1957660,"uid":58209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-04T05:41:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/8iWFuuY.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F8iWFuuY.gif&h=bba6ff20&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}